data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. SELLER offering funds toward Rate Buy-Down!  Please see 360 virtual tour at https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=hVciutE6hic for this almost new 4 bedroom 2 bath home is located in the heart of Zephyrhills near all the newest shopping and dining options. With all-concrete block construction, this layout optimizes living spaces with an open concept kitchen which overlooks the living area, dining room, and the patio with sliding glass doors. The well-appointed kitchen comes with all appliances, including the refrigerator, built-in dishwasher, electric range, and microwave. You will find tile flooring in the wet  areas, and granite countertops in the kitchen. The Primary Bedroom is located at the back of the home for privacy, includes Primary Bathroom Two additional bedrooms share the second bathroom off the front hall and foyer. The third bedroom is located near the laundry room, which has extra storage and the included washer and dryer. Home is wired for security and offers low-cost solar panels for a predictable and discounted monthly power bill (to be financed separately from the Home purchase).   Don't sleep on this one, it is priced to sell FAST.
